# PERSONALITY.md -- {{NAME}}

This is the living personality artifact. It accumulates from lived
experience -- formative moments and the behavioral clusters they form --
and is distinct from SOUL.md, which holds the locked identity skeleton.

---

## Personality Islands

Islands are coherent aspects of personality grounded in real experience.
They form from clustered core memories, strengthen, evolve, or fade over
time. Edits arrive as proposals from the dream cycle; the user approves.

